        <name xml:lang="en">Ammonium</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">The remaining amount of unreacted ammonia is assumed to leave the production process with the waste water. Further it was assumed that this wastewater is treated in a internal wastewater plant. For the ammonia within the waste water a removal efficiency of 50% was assumed. The nitrogen emitted to air (N2) and remaining in the sewage sludge was neglected.</comment>
